@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dublyg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.98
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.exp(v0 + 0.77) * v2))
    tmp = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.06 / v1 + 0.07) / (v2 + 0.15 / v0 + 0.73)))
    v0 = v1
    v0 = (tmp - (0.71 + v0))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.90)) + wp.exp(0.09))
    data[tid] = v0
